Class UserInterface

  • java.lang.Object
    • ui.UserInterface
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CommandLineInterface, GUI

    public abstract class UserInterface
extends java.lang.Object
    An user interface manager that abstracts the implementation of the user interaction. It is an abstract class for GUI and command line interface
